<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Capacity on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/capacity/</link><description>Recent content in Capacity on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/capacity/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] AWS DynamoDB — ProvisionedThroughputExceededException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/aws/aws-dynamodb-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/aws/aws-dynamodb-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A ProvisionedThroughputExceededException means the DynamoDB table or index has exceeded its provisioned read or write capacity units. DynamoDB throttles requests that exceed the allocated throughput.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DynamoDB tables can run in Provisioned or On-Demand capacity mode. In Provisioned mode, you specify read capacity units (RCUs) and write capacity units (WCUs). When request volume exceeds these limits, DynamoDB returns &lt;code&gt;ProvisionedThroughputExceededException&lt;/code&gt;. Each partition has its own throughput limit, so hot partitions can cause throttling even when total table capacity is not exceeded. The error includes &lt;code&gt;RequestItems&lt;/code&gt; showing which tables/indexes were throttled.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Azure VM — allocation failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/azure/azure-vm-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/azure/azure-vm-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;An Azure VM allocation failed error means Azure cannot allocate the requested VM SKU in the specified region and availability zone. The deployment fails due to insufficient capacity or quota limits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Azure allocates VM resources from its global infrastructure. When you request a VM with a specific SKU (e.g., Standard_D4s_v5) in a region, Azure checks for available physical capacity and your subscription&amp;rsquo;s quota. If either is exhausted, the allocation fails with &lt;code&gt;AllocationFailed&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;SkuNotAvailable&lt;/code&gt;. This is distinct from quota limits — it means Azure literally does not have enough physical hardware in that region for the requested VM size.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::length_error - string too long</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-string/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-string/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="stdlength_error---string-too-long"&gt;std::length_error - string too long&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::length_error&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a &lt;code&gt;std::string&lt;/code&gt; operation would create a string longer than &lt;code&gt;std::string::max_size()&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Concatenation overflow
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string s(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10000000000LL&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Reserve too much
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string s;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;s.reserve(SIZE_MAX); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Append causing overflow
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;s.append(std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;npos, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;x&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-size-before-operation"&gt;Fix 1: Check size before operation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (s.size() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; add_size &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; s.max_size()) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; s.append(add);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-streaming"&gt;Fix 2: Use streaming&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string result;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; chunk : chunks) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; chunk; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// grows incrementally
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-catch-and-handle"&gt;Fix 3: Catch and handle&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string s(huge_size, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;length_error&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cerr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;String too long: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; e.what() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-vector/"&gt;std::length_error - vector&lt;/a&gt; — vector too large.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-map/"&gt;std::length_error - map&lt;/a&gt; — map max size.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/bad-alloc-nostd/"&gt;std::bad_alloc&lt;/a&gt; — allocation failure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::length_error - vector resize too large</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-vector/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-vector/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="stdlength_error---vector-resize-too-large"&gt;std::length_error - vector resize too large&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::length_error&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a &lt;code&gt;std::vector::resize()&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;reserve()&lt;/code&gt; call exceeds the maximum possible size.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Resize to max size
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; v;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;v.resize(std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;numeric_limits&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;size_t&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;::&lt;/span&gt;max()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Reserve overflow
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; v;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;v.reserve(SIZE_MAX); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// throws
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Huge allocation request
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; v(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100000000000LL&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// may throw
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-size-limit"&gt;Fix 1: Check size limit&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (n &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; v.max_size()) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; v.resize(n);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-try-catch"&gt;Fix 2: Use try-catch&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; v.resize(n);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;length_error&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cerr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Too large: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; e.what() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-smaller-chunks"&gt;Fix 3: Use smaller chunks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; v;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (size_t i &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;; i &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; n; i &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; chunk_size) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; size_t end &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;min(i &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; chunk_size, n);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; v.resize(end);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/bad-alloc-nostd/"&gt;std::bad_alloc&lt;/a&gt; — allocation failure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/length-error-string/"&gt;std::length_error - string&lt;/a&gt; — string too long.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/out-of-range-vector/"&gt;std::out_of_range&lt;/a&gt; — index out of range.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Go Slice Bounds Out of Range — Runtime Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/slice-bounds-out-of-range/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/slice-bounds-out-of-range/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="slice-bounds-out-of-range--runtime-error-fix"&gt;Slice Bounds Out of Range — Runtime Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A slice bounds out of range panic occurs when a slice expression uses bounds that exceed the slice&amp;rsquo;s length or capacity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Go, slice expressions &lt;code&gt;s[low:high]&lt;/code&gt; require &lt;code&gt;0 &amp;lt;= low &amp;lt;= high &amp;lt;= cap(s)&lt;/code&gt;. If &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; exceeds the capacity or &lt;code&gt;low&lt;/code&gt; exceeds &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt;, the runtime panics with &lt;code&gt;runtime error: slice bounds out of range&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Slicing beyond capacity&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;s[:100]&lt;/code&gt; when &lt;code&gt;cap(s)&lt;/code&gt; is 50.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Slicing with reversed bounds&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;s[5:2]&lt;/code&gt; where low &amp;gt; high.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Slicing a nil slice&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;var s []int; s[0:5]&lt;/code&gt; panics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Using &lt;code&gt;append&lt;/code&gt; result without checking&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;append&lt;/code&gt; may return a new slice with different capacity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Slicing beyond capacity&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; make([]&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// panic: slice bounds out of range [2:10] with capacity 5&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Reversed bounds&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// panic: slice bounds out of range [2:1]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Nil slice slicing&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// panic: slice bounds out of range [0:5] with length 0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Slicing after append that grows the backing array&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; make([]&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; = append(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// capacity used up&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Original capacity reference is stale&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// panic&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-capacity-before-slicing-beyond-length"&gt;Fix 1: Check capacity before slicing beyond length&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; cap(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:cap(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;)]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-ensure-low--high-in-slice-expressions"&gt;Fix 2: Ensure low &amp;lt;= high in slice expressions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sliceRange&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sliceRange&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;low&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;high&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-initialize-slices-before-slicing"&gt;Fix 3: Initialize slices before slicing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; make([]&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-the-three-index-slice-to-limit-capacity"&gt;Fix 4: Use the three-index slice to limit capacity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong — may accidentally share backing array&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;)]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — explicitly control capacity&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sub&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;):len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;)]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-5-check-length-before-slicing"&gt;Fix 5: Check length before slicing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;firstN&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// panics if n &amp;gt; len(s)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;firstN&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; = len(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[:&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This triggers: runtime error: slice bounds out of range [5:3] with length 4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fmt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt; []&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fmt&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/index-out-of-range/"&gt;index-out-of-range&lt;/a&gt; — accessing a single index beyond the slice length.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/nil-pointer/"&gt;nil-pointer&lt;/a&gt; — dereferencing a nil pointer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/out-of-memory/"&gt;out-of-memory&lt;/a&gt; — allocating too much memory with large slices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Go Slice Bounds Out of Range — Runtime Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/slice-bounds/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/go/slice-bounds/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="slice-bounds-out-of-range--runtime-error"&gt;Slice Bounds Out of Range — Runtime Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The error &lt;code&gt;runtime error: slice bounds out of range&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you use a slice expression (&lt;code&gt;s[low:high]&lt;/code&gt;) where &lt;code&gt;low&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; exceeds the slice&amp;rsquo;s length or capacity, or where &lt;code&gt;low &amp;gt; high&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When reslicing in Go, the bounds must satisfy: &lt;code&gt;0 &amp;lt;= low &amp;lt;= high &amp;lt;= cap(s)&lt;/code&gt;. If &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; exceeds the capacity or &lt;code&gt;low&lt;/code&gt; is greater than &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt;, Go panics at runtime. This differs from index-out-of-range errors because it involves slice expressions rather than single-element access.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>GCP Compute Engine: The Zone Does Not Have Enough Resources</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/gcp/compute-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/gcp/compute-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;The zone does not have enough resources&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when a Google Cloud zone has insufficient capacity for the requested resource (e.g., specific machine type, GPU, or SSD). This is a temporary capacity issue, not a quota limit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The zone has a shortage of the requested machine type (e.g., &lt;code&gt;n2-standard-8&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GPU resources are exhausted in the zone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SSD/local SSD capacity is fully allocated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High demand period (e.g., Black Friday) causes temporary capacity shortages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Try a different zone:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>